Second version of an OCR.

Currently just a graphic lib with some examples.
There are buttons, text areas, cursors and you can create multiple frames.
You can also drop an image.

There are some categories accessible with the MENU button.
Each category is a different frame, there is the tutorial (how to use the app),
the OCR, the training (of the OCR) and some credits.


